{
  "texts": [
    "We first consider an off-the-shelf instruction tuned model: Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.2.",
    "This model based on Mistral-7B achieves comparable performance to Llama 2 13B Chat on the MT-Bench (Zheng et al., 2023).",
    "In addition, we train Mistral-7B and Llama 2 models on the T0 split from the P3 dataset (Bach et al., 2022) and adapt them to the target tasks.",
    "We call these models Mistral-7B P3 and Llama 2 P3.",
    "For the instruction tuning details, see Appendix F. 2 Training Details We fine-tune the language models on the supervision sources-TAPT, and Table 3: Results for zero-shot task adaptation of instruction tuned models."
  ]
}